quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  30,1,Alif-Laam-Meem
  30,2,Roomi maghloob hogaye hain
  30,3,Nazdeek ki zamin per aur woh maghloon honey kay baad un-qareeb ghalib aajayen gay
  30,4,Chand saal mein hi. Iss say pehlay aur iss kay baad bhi ikhtiyar Allah Taalaa hi ka hai. Uss roz musalman shaadmaan hongay
  30,5,Allah ki madad say woh jiss ki chahata hai madad kerta hai. Asal ghalin aur meharbaan wohi hai
  30,6,Allah ka wada hai Allah Taalaa apnay waday kay khilaf nahi kerta lekin aksar log nahi jantay
  30,7,Woh to (sirf) duniyawi zindagi kay zahir ko (hi) jantay hain aur aakhirat say to bilkul hi bay khabar hain
  30,8,Kiya inn logon ney apnay dil mein yeh ghor nahi kiya? Kay Allah Taalaa ney aasmano ko aur zamin aur inn kay darmiyan jo kuch hai sab ko behtareen qareeney say muqarrar waqt tak kay liye hi (peda) kiya hai haan aksar log yaqeenan apnay rab ki mulaqat kay munkir hain
  30,9,Kiya enhon ney zamin mein chal phir ker yeh nahi dekha kay inn say pehlay logon ka anjam kaisa (bura) hua? Woh inn say boht zada tawana (aur taqatwar) thay aur unhon ney (bhi) zamin boee joti thi aur inn say ziyada abad ki thi aur unn kay pass unkay rasool roshan dalaeel ley ker aaye thay. Yeh to na mumkin tha kayAllah Taalaa unn per zulm kerta lekin (dar asal) woh khud apni jano per zulm kertay thay
  30,10,Phir aakhrish bura kerney walon ka boht hi bura anjam hua iss liye kay woh Allah Taalaa ki aayaton ko jhutlatay thay aur inn ki hansi uratay thay
  30,11,Allah Taalaa hi makhlooq ki ibtida kerta hai phir wohi ussay doobara peda keray ga phir tum sab ussi ki taraf lotaye jaogay
  30,12,Aur jiss din qayamat qaeem hogi to gunehgaar heyrat zada reh jayen gay
  30,13,Aur inn kay tamam tar shareekon mein say aik bhi inn ka sifarshi na hoga aur (khud yeh bhi) apnay shareekon kay munkir ho jayen gay
  30,14,Aur jiss din qayamat qaeem hogi uss din (jamaten) alag alag hojayen gi
  30,15,Jo eman laa ker nek aemaal kertay rahey woh to jannat mein khush-o-khurram ker diyey jayen gay
  30,16,Aur jinhon ney kufur kiya tha aur humari aayaton ko aur aakhirat ki mulaqat ko jhoota theraya tha woh sab azab mein pakar ker hazir rakhay jayen gay
  30,17,Pus Allah Taalaa ki tasbeeh parha kero jab kay tum shaam kero aur jab subah kero
  30,18,Tamam tareefon kay laeeq aasman-o-zamin mein sirf wohi hai teesray pehar bhi aur zohar kay waqt bhi (uss ki pakeezgi biyan kero)
  30,19,(wohi) zinda ko murda say aur murda ko zinda say nikalta hai. Aur wohi zamin ko uss ki maut kay baad zinda kerta hai issi tarah tum (bhi) nikalay jao gay
  30,20,Allah ki nishaniyon mein say hai kay uss ney tum ko mitti say peda kiya phir abb insan bann ker (chaltay phirtay) phel rahey ho
  30,21,Aur uss ki nishaniyon mein say hai kay tumhari hi jins say biwiyan peda ki takay tum inn say aaram pao uss ney tumharay darmiyan mohabbat aur humdardi qaeem kerdi yaqeenan ghor-o-fiker kerney walon kay liye iss mein boht si nishaniyan hain
  30,22,Uss (ki qudrat) ki nishaniyon mein say aasmano aur zamin ki pedaeesh aur tumhari zabano aur rangaton ka ikhtilaf (bhi) hai danish mando kay liye iss mein yaqeenan bari nishaniyan hain
  30,23,Aur (bhi) uss ki (qudrat ki) nishani tumhari raton aur din ki neend mein hai aur uss kay fazal (yani rozi) ko tumhara talash kerna bhi hai. Jo log (kaan laga ker) sunnay kay aadi hain unn kay liye iss mein boht si nishaniyan hain
  30,24,Aur uss ki nishaniyon mein say aik yeh (bhi) hai kay woh tumhen daraney aur umeedwaar bananay kay liye bijliyan dikhata hai aur aasman say barish barsata hai aur iss say murda zamin ko zinda ker deta hai iss mein (bhi) aqal mando kay liye boht si nishaniyan hain
  30,25,Uss ki aik nishani yeh bhi hai kay aasman-o-zamin ussi kay hukum say qaeem hain phir jab woh tumhen awaz dey ga sirf aik baar ki awaz kay sath hi tum sab zamin say nikal aao gay
  30,26,Aur aasman-o-zamin ki her her cheez ussi ki milkiyat hai aur her aik ussi kay farman kay ma-tehat hai
  30,27,Wohi hai jo awwal baar makhlooq ko peda kerta hai phir ussay doobara peda keray ga aur yeh to uss per boht aasaan hai. Ussi ki behtareen aur aalaa sift hai aasmano aur zamin mein bhi aur wohi ghalbay wala hikmat wala hai
  30,28,Allah Taalaa ney tumharay liye aik misaal khud tumhari hi biyan farmaee jo kuch hum ney tumhen dey rakha hai kiya uss mein tumharay ghulamon mein say bhi koi tumhara shareek hai? Kiya tum aur woh iss mein barabar darjay kay ho? Aur tum inn ka aisa khatra rakhtay ho jaisa khud apno ka hum aqal rakhney walon kay liye issi tarah khol khol ker aayaten biyan ker detay hain
  30,29,Bulkay baat yeh hai kay yeh zalim to baghair ilm kay khuwaish parasti ker rahey hain ussay kaun raah dikhaye jissay Allah Taalaa raah say hata dey unn ka aik bhi madadgaar nahi
  30,30,Pus aap yeksoo hoker apna mun deen ki taraf mutawajja ker den. Allah Taalaa ki woh fitrat jiss per uss ney logon ko peda kiya hai Allah Taalaa kay banaye ko badlna nahi yehi seedah deen hai lekin aksar log nahi samajhtay